name: Fech The Ferret & OKAMI
description:
Fech The Ferret

OKAMI is a very popular german chatbotproject on Whatsapp that exists since August 2020.
After being wiped 4x, the r/Greenlattice provided a space next to "Fech the ferret".
As a thank you, the OKAMI community included the videogame character into the artwork.
